Subject: [PATCH 1735/2066] Revert "arm64: dts: r8a7796-salvator-x: Add VSP
 Manager support"

This reverts commit 20b1a791d48f ("arm64: dts: r8a7796-salvator-x: Add
VSP Manager support").

This reverted commit has deleted VIN0 device node, without meaning at
the same time it adds VSP Manager node.

The patch which only VSP Manager node adds is added later.

